.SM "INQUIRE DEPTH CUE REPRESENTATION (3P+)"
.SM "INQUIRE DEPTH CUE FACILITIES (3P+)"
.SM "INQUIRE LIST OF DEPTH CUE INDICES (3P+)"
.fi
